The hetras API is using this [Patch Specification](https://developer.hetras.com/docs/patch) to partially update an existing resource. Currently this call only allows to modify condition and housekeeping occupancy status of the room.  

A request example:  

            [
              {
                "op": "replace", "path": "/status/condition", "value": "CleanNotInspected"
              }, {
                "op": "replace", "path": "/status/housekeeping_occupancy", "value": "Vacant"
              }
            ]


For more details on how the API responds to errors please check our documentation on [Error Handling](https://developer.hetras.com/docs/errors/).
